:"1"},"index":0},{"ChoiceID":"1","Grades":{"SC_9Rb0HikouMWnL5Y":"0"},"index":1}],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":1,"NextChoiceId":4,"QuestionDescription":"Claim 4 of 10 Cleopatra lived around 30 BCE, roughly 2,500 years after the Great Pyramid of Giza...","QuestionText":"Claim 4 of 10<br>Cleopatra lived around 30 BCE, roughly 2,500 years after the Great Pyramid of Giza was built. The Moon landing occurred in 1969, about 2,000 years after her lifetime. This surprising timeline reshapes how we think about the ancient world and the sheer age of Egyptian Civilization.","QuestionText_Unsafe":"Claim 4 of 10<br>Security researchers estimate that credential-stuffing attacks \u2014 in which stolen username and password pairs are tested across multiple platforms \u2014 account for approximately 30% of login attempts on major websites.","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function() {\n    var textContainer = this.getQuestionTextContainer();\n\n    \/\/ Get the original question text\n    var fullText = textContainer.innerText.trim();\n    var words = fullText.split(\/\\s+\/);\n\n    \/\/ Clear the text\n    textContainer.innerHTML = \"\";\n\n    \/\/ Total reveal time = 10 seconds\n    var totalRevealTime = 10000;\n    var wordSpeed = Math.max(50, Math.floor(totalRevealTime \/ words.length));\n\n    var i = 0;\n\n    function typeWord() {\n        if (i < words.length) {\n            textContainer.innerHTML += words[i] + \" \";\n            i++;\n            setTimeout(typeWord, wordSpeed);\n        }\n    }\n\n    typeWord();\n});","DataExportTag":"Tech2","QuestionID":"QID238"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_3UyxHHFTl7Y7X5c","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID239","SecondaryAttribute":"How confident are you when you were making the choice?","TertiaryAttribute":null,"Payload":{"QuestionText":"How confident are you when you were making the choice?","DefaultCho