,{"ChoiceID":"2","Grades":{"SC_9Rb0HikouMWnL5Y":"1"},"index":1}],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":1,"NextChoiceId":4,"QuestionDescription":"Claim 6 of 10 It is widely reported that humans share roughly 60% of their DNA with bananas. Whil...","QuestionText":"Claim 6 of 10<br>It is widely reported that humans share roughly 60% of their DNA with bananas. While genetic research shows significant overlap across all living organisms due to shared evolutionary origins, the way this statistic gets communicated often leaves out important context about what genetic similarity actually means at a functional level.","QuestionText_Unsafe":"Claim 6 of 10<br>It is widely reported that humans share roughly 60% of their DNA with bananas. While genetic research shows significant overlap across all living organisms due to shared evolutionary origins, the way this statistic gets communicated often leaves out important context about what genetic similarity actually means at a functional level.","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function() {\n    var textContainer = this.getQuestionTextContainer();\n\n    \/\/ Get the original question text\n    var fullText = textContainer.innerText.trim();\n    var words = fullText.split(\/\\s+\/);\n\n    \/\/ Clear the text\n    textContainer.innerHTML = \"\";\n\n    \/\/ Total reveal time = 5 seconds\n    var totalRevealTime = 5000;\n    var wordSpeed = Math.max(30, Math.floor(totalRevealTime \/ words.length));\n\n    var i = 0;\n\n    function typeWord() {\n        if (i < words.length) {\n            textContainer.innerHTML += words[i] + \" \";\n            i++;\n            setTimeout(typeWord, wordSpeed);\n        }\n    }\n\n    typeWord();\n});","DataExportTag":"AS6","QuestionID":"QID595"}},{"SurveyID":"SV_3UyxHHFTl7Y7X5c","Element":"SQ","PrimaryAttribute":"QID596","SecondaryAttribute":"How confidence were you in th