hare Now"},"2":{"Display":"Verify First"}},"Configuration":{"QuestionDescriptionOption":"UseText"},"DataVisibility":{"Hidden":false,"Private":false},"DefaultChoices":false,"GradingData":[{"ChoiceID":"2","Grades":{"SC_9Rb0HikouMWnL5Y":"1"},"index":0},{"ChoiceID":"1","Grades":{"SC_9Rb0HikouMWnL5Y":"0"},"index":1}],"Language":[],"NextAnswerId":1,"NextChoiceId":4,"QuestionDescription":"Claim 7 of 10 Various health researchers have estimated that, across an average lifespan, a perso...","QuestionText":"Claim 7 of 10<br>Various health researchers have estimated that, across an average lifespan, a person may walk anywhere from 75,000 to more than 100,000 miles. Some studies frame this as roughly equivalent to circling the Earth multiple times, though the exact figure varies widely depending on lifestyle, geography, and overall health habits.","QuestionText_Unsafe":"Claim 7 of 10<br>Various health researchers have estimated that, across an average lifespan, a person may walk anywhere from 75,000 to more than 100,000 miles. Some studies frame this as roughly equivalent to circling the Earth multiple times, though the exact figure varies widely depending on lifestyle, geography, and overall health habits.","QuestionType":"MC","Selector":"SAVR","SubSelector":"TX","Validation":{"Settings":{"ForceResponse":"OFF","Type":"None"}},"QuestionJS":"Qualtrics.SurveyEngine.addOnReady(function() {\n    var textContainer = this.getQuestionTextContainer();\n\n    \/\/ Get the original question text\n    var fullText = textContainer.innerText.trim();\n    var words = fullText.split(\/\\s+\/);\n\n    \/\/ Clear the text\n    textContainer.innerHTML = \"\";\n\n    \/\/ Total reveal time = 5 seconds\n    var totalRevealTime = 5000;\n    var wordSpeed = Math.max(30, Math.floor(totalRevealTime \/ words.length));\n\n    var i = 0;\n\n    function typeWord() {\n        if (i < words.length) {\n            textContainer.innerHTML += words[i] + \" \";\n            i++;\n            setTimeout(typeWor